   <head>Aduertisements.</head>
   <p>FIrst yee shall finde a worde in <milestone type="tcpmilestone" unit="unspecified" n="1"/> the margent opposite to each Resolution, to shew vnto what Principle of Religion your case and answer doth belong.</p>
   <p>The cases and answers for the <milestone type="tcpmilestone" unit="unspecified" n="2"/> most part doe follow the order and dependance which the Prin<g ref="char:EOLhyphen"/>ciples haue amongst themselues.</p>
